&lt;div style=&quot;text-align: right;&quot;&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;SClippy has been downloaded!&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;blockquote&gt;
&lt;p&gt;i&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/blockquote&gt;
&lt;table class=&quot;wiki-content-table&quot;&gt;
&lt;tr&gt;
&lt;td&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Hold Up! You’ve made a mistake! Your device has Auto-Grammar turned off! Luckily, I can fix it! You also need to make it bold. To do it, put two asterisks (&lt;span style=&quot;white-space: pre-wrap;&quot;&gt;**&lt;/span&gt;) before and after your writing! I’ve automatically fives this!&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/td&gt;
&lt;/tr&gt;
&lt;/table&gt;
&lt;blockquote&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;white-space: pre-wrap;&quot;&gt;**Item**&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/blockquote&gt;
&lt;blockquote&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;white-space: pre-wrap;&quot;&gt;**Item**&lt;/span&gt; #:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/blockquote&gt;
&lt;table class=&quot;wiki-content-table&quot;&gt;
&lt;tr&gt;
&lt;td&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Hold Up! You need to make both the hashtag (#) and colon (:) bold too! To do i&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/td&gt;
&lt;/tr&gt;
&lt;/table&gt;
&lt;blockquote&gt;
&lt;p&gt;I can do this now, thanks.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/blockquote&gt;
&lt;table class=&quot;wiki-content-table&quot;&gt;
&lt;tr&gt;
&lt;td&gt;&lt;strong&gt;No problem! ^.^ SClippy’s here to help!&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/td&gt;
&lt;/tr&gt;
&lt;/table&gt;
&lt;blockquote&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;white-space: pre-wrap;&quot;&gt;**Item&amp;#32;#:**&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/blockquote&gt;
&lt;blockquote&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;white-space: pre-wrap;&quot;&gt;**Item&amp;#32;#:**&lt;/span&gt; SCP-9&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/blockquote&gt;
&lt;table class=&quot;wiki-content-table&quot;&gt;
&lt;tr&gt;
&lt;td&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Hold Up! You can’t personally assign your SCP a designation &lt;em&gt;yet&lt;/em&gt;! I’ve helped you out!&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/td&gt;
&lt;/tr&gt;
&lt;/table&gt;
&lt;blockquote&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;white-space: pre-wrap;&quot;&gt;**Item&amp;#32;#:**&lt;/span&gt; SCP-XXXX&lt;/p&gt;
