&lt;div class=&quot;collapsible-block-content&quot;&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div style=&quot;text-align: left;&quot;&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;&lt;span&gt;what&#039;s this?&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Underread and Underrated is a project intended to shine a spotlight on, well, underread and underrated pages!&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;&lt;span&gt;oh neat. What&#039;s the blurb for?&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;As part of the associated UaU initiative, each month we&#039;ll be picking an element of SCP lore that people outside the general gestalt might not know about. We&#039;re also hosting writing challenges involving said lore!&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;&lt;span&gt;may i suggest [blank] for the topic?&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Sure! Do note, however, that anything with a dedicated hub&lt;sup class=&quot;footnoteref&quot;&gt;&lt;a id=&quot;footnoteref-610159-1&quot; href=&quot;javascript:;&quot; class=&quot;footnoteref&quot;  &gt;1&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/sup&gt; above +100 in rating can&#039;t be made topic. Sorry! D:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Suggestions should be PM&#039;d to &lt;span class=&quot;printuser avatarhover&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/uraniumempire&quot;  &gt;&lt;img class=&quot;small&quot; src=&quot;http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=1613974&amp;amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;amp;timestamp=1610204913&quot; alt=&quot;UraniumEmpire&quot; style=&quot;background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=1613974)&quot; /&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/uraniumempire&quot;  &gt;UraniumEmpire&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt;!&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;&lt;span&gt;oh cool how do i participate?&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Just PM &lt;span class=&quot;printuser avatarhover&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/uraniumempire&quot;  &gt;&lt;img class=&quot;small&quot; src=&quot;http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=1613974&amp;amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;amp;timestamp=1610204913&quot; alt=&quot;UraniumEmpire&quot; style=&quot;background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=1613974)&quot; /&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/uraniumempire&quot;  &gt;UraniumEmpire&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt; a link to your piece and she&#039;ll post it on next month&#039;s &amp;quot;Last Month&#039;s Pieces and Topic&amp;quot; section!&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;For artists: try to link to whatever social media page is hosting the art. It saves us space and ensures we have a solid reference.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
